      <title>据称沙特支持的 LIV 高尔夫公司正在考虑与 DP 世界巡回赛达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/saudi-backed-liv-golf-is-said-to-weigh-deal-with-dp-world-tour</link>
